Authour: @librehat
Twitter: @librehat
Web Site: http://www.librehat.co.cc

English:
You should have the access to write files under this directory and your working directory.
Put all files in /sysmte/app to "app" directory and /system/framwork to "framework" directory.
Suggestion:
	Also make a copy of framework to "bootclasspathdir" directory. More technical details, please see the project "smali".
You NEED to sign and align all the output apk and jar files after this operation.

NOTICE: Some apk such as Phone.apk and Email.apk couldn't be re-builded by apktool.You can use classical_deodex_tool to merge them.

简体中文/Simplified Chinese:
你应该有本目录和工作目录（支持在其它目录下执行本脚本）的写入权限。
将/system/app下的全部文件放入app目录，将/system/framework下的放入framework目录。
建议：
	复制一份framework的内容到bootclasspathdir目录。关于更多技术细节，请查阅smali项目。
全部完成后，请记得用HatMod提供的批量签名优化工具对合并后的文件进行重新签名。